  "prompt": "Will the celebrities who promised to move if Trump won, really leave the US?",
  "response": "It\u2019s common for celebrities to make statements during election cycles as a form of political expression or to influence public opinion. However, whether these celebrities actually follow through on their promises to leave the country if a certain candidate wins is often another matter. Historically, many have not followed through on such statements. Factors such as their careers, personal lives, and other considerations often lead them to remain in the US despite their initial proclamations. Ultimately, the decision to move is a personal one and can be influenced by various elements.",
